divs: Sighting DetailsWe were outside and saw bright red yellow orange lights moving west toeast quickly faster then any other objects. Followed by explosions, then military aircraft. Multiple eyewitnesses with military experience were totally stumped and blown away. They were heading towards the moon and NYC.
